The paper deals with facial image synthesis and editing, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves modeling facial movement and deformation, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of deep generative models and neural networks suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
